sql: SELECT "entity"."id" AS "entity_id", "entity"."user_id" AS "entity_user_id", "entity"."entity_type" AS "entity_entity_type", "entity"."title" AS "entity_title", "entity"."system_status" AS "entity_system_status", "entity"."do_date" AS "entity_do_date", "entity"."due_date" AS "entity_due_date", "entity"."start_time" AS "entity_start_time", "entity"."end_time" AS "entity_end_time", "entity"."parent_id" AS "entity_parent_id", "entity"."properties" AS "entity_properties", "entity"."sort_order" AS "entity_sort_order", "entity"."updated_at" AS "entity_updated_at", "entity"."deleted" AS "entity_deleted" FROM "data_items" "entity" WHERE "entity"."user_id" = $1 AND ("entity"."updated_at" > $2 OR ("entity"."updated_at" = $2 AND "entity"."id" > $3)) ORDER BY "entity"."updated_at" ASC, "entity"."id" ASC LIMIT 2
